cd tinyboxes
heroku create
git push heroku master
heroku config:add FB_APP_ID=<your fb app id> FB_APP_SECRET=<your fb app secret>

# e.g. for testing:
heroku config:add FB_PAGE_NAME="pages/Tiny-Boxes-Test-Page/108040335960818"
# e.g. for production:
heroku config:add FB_PAGE_NAME="unicef"

Example fb app config:
---------------------

Canvas URL: http://tinyboxes-demo.heroku.com/
Tab URL: http://tinyboxes-demo.heroku.com/leaderboard




